@startuml CoreNeedleBiopsy_Workflow_ReflexTesting
title Szenario 3: Nachforderung / Reflex-Untersuchung\nCore Needle Biopsy – IHC nach ASAP-Befund

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #AAAAAA
skinparam sequenceGroupFontSize 11
skinparam noteFontSize 10
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8DC

participant "**Placer (KIS)**\nUrologie" as Placer #BDD7EE
participant "**Filler (LIS)**\nPathologie" as Filler #C6EFCE

== Auftragserstellung (2024-01-15, 08:00) ==

Placer -> Filler : POST Bundle (type: **transaction**)\n  Patient\n  ServiceRequest (status: **active**)\n  Specimen [x12] (status: **available**)\n  Task (status: **requested**, code: fulfill)
activate Filler
Filler --> Placer : Bundle (type: **transaction-response**)\n  201 Created
deactivate Filler

note over Placer, Filler : **Coordination Task V1: requested**

== Probenempfang & Annahme (2024-01-15, 14:00) ==

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task (status: **accepted**)

note over Placer, Filler : **Coordination Task V2: accepted**

== Bearbeitung beginnt (2024-01-16, 08:00) ==

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task (status: **in-progress**)

note over Placer, Filler : **Coordination Task V3: in-progress**

group Pathologische Aufarbeitung
  Filler -> Filler : Makroskopie
  Filler -> Filler : Mikroskopie (HE)
end

== ASAP-Befund – IHC erforderlich (2024-01-18, 10:00) ==

note over Filler : Stanze 03: Atypische\nDrusenproliferation (ASAP)\n\nEntscheidung: p63/AMACR-\nDoppelfaerbung zur Abklaerung

Filler -> Filler : Neuer ServiceRequest erstellen\n(code: IHC p63/AMACR\nbasedOn: Original-ServiceRequest\nstatus: **active**)

Filler -> Filler : Aliquot-Specimen erstellen\n(type: Tissue section\nparent: Block03\nprocessing: p63/AMACR immunostain)

Filler -> Filler : Interner Task\n(status: **requested**\nfocus: IHC-ServiceRequest\ninput: Aliquot-Specimen)

note over Filler #E8F4FD : **Reflex-Untersuchung laeuft intern**\nFiller ist Placer UND Filler\nfuer die IHC-Zusatzuntersuchung

group IHC-Aufarbeitung [1-2 Tage]
  Filler -> Filler : Schnittherstellung\n(vom Block03)
  Filler -> Filler : p63/AMACR-Doppelfaerbung
  Filler -> Filler : Mikroskopische Beurteilung\nErgebnis: AMACR positiv,\np63 negativ -> Karzinom bestaetigt
end

== Gesamtbefund & Abschluss (2024-01-20, 15:30) ==

Filler -> Filler : DiagnosticReport erstellen\n(inkl. IHC-Ergebnis fuer Stanze 03)

Filler -> Placer : POST Bundle (type: **document**, signed)\n  Composition\n  DiagnosticReport (status: **final**)\n  Patient, ServiceRequest, Specimen\n  Observations (inkl. IHC-Findings)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 201 Created
deactivate Placer

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task\n(status: **completed**\noutput: Bundle)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

note over Placer, Filler : **Coordination Task V4: completed**\nBefund enthaelt HE + IHC Ergebnisse

Placer -> Placer : ServiceRequest\n(status: **completed**)

note over Placer : Befund im KIS:\nAdenokarzinom in Stanze 03\ndurch IHC bestaetigt\n(AMACR+, p63-)

@enduml
